際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"edf8538c1c6d8c84b1a5ad315bcf2ae2885c45aa","tid":1913233,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"好想抽插佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bb743a8289873fe419334c21f29f05c16bf562","tid":1913233,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}